FBIS3-16554 "drsov052_f_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-052 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Mar 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk Reverses Meshkov Decision on Referendum LD1603153094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1400 GMT 16 Mar 94 LD1603153094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Leonid Kravchuk, president of the Ukraine, has reversed a decision taken by Yuriy Meshkov, president of Crimea, to ask Crimeans about its position with regard to the Ukraine. This decision has been qualified as being contrary to the Ukrainian constitution and laws.
